            <p class="testimonial-text">"PRISM has transformed how we manage our operations. The efficiency gains have been remarkable."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
                <div class="author-avatar"></div>
                <div>
                    <div class="author-name">Sarah Mitchell</div>
                    <div class="author-title">COO, TechCorp Solutions</div>
                </div>
